verbose_text: The data included the first author 's name, year of publication, study population, country of origin, sample size, proportion of men, duration of follow-up, range or mean of participants ' age, number of events, case identification methods, categories of fish or LCn3PUFA intake, the amount of fish or LCn3PUFA intake for each category, methods for diet measurement, adjusted covariates, as well as RRs and 95% CIs of incident diabetes in the corresponding categories.
